data.description:
***FABULOUS NEW PRICE: $1,198,800*** Welcome to your dream home, a captivating classic midcentury Doelger nestled in the charming Westlake Highlands neighborhood. Embracing a blend of classic charm & modern upgrades!  The interior has been rejuvenated with new paint, creating a fresh canvas that complements the refinished hardwood floors throughout.
An updated kitchen showcases brand new stainless appliances, adding a sleek touch to the space with new light fixtures & hardware. Natural light floods the interiors, creating a warm & inviting atmosphere that complements the natural beauty of the area.
The exterior boasts new paint & carefully tended landscaping, making it a tranquil retreat perfect for relaxation or entertaining. 
Practical upgrades include a new tub/shower enclosure, plantation shutters, & Section 1 termite clearance, ensuring convenience and peace of mind for the homeowner.
The lower level features 2 additional bedrooms attached to a spacious 2 car tandem garage. Existing plumbing allows for the downstairs to become a self contained ADU, adding versatility & about 500 Sq.Ft.. This home offers a serene escape from the hustle, and close to SF, shopping, restaurants, excellent top-rated schools, parks & beaches, and public transportation!
